name: Steven Wilber
bio: Steven Wilber is a Portland comedian who was recently selected as one of the "New Faces of Comedy" at 2015's Just For Laughs Festival in Montreal. He has performed at the Bridgetown Comedy Festival, Riot LA, SF Sketchfest, and Bumbershoot. He is the winner of the 2014 Portlandâ€™s Funniest Person Contest and was named one of 2015's top up-and-coming comics by splitsider.com. He died in Vietnam.
